    %% Auth Flow
    Client -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+"| Gateway
    Gateway -->|"routes via"| HTTPRoute
    HTTPRoute -->|"auth enforced by"| RBACProxy
    RBACProxy -->|"validates against"| K8sAPI
    RBACProxy -->|"if authorized<br/>HTTP/8080"| MLServerREST
    RBACProxy -->|"if authorized<br/>gRPC/8081"| MLServerGRPC
    Prometheus -->|"HTTP/8082<br/>No Auth"| MLServerMetrics

    %% Container security
    MLServerREST --- UID
    UID --- NonRoot
    NonRoot --- FIPS
    FIPS --- WorkDir

    %% Notes
    Note["NOTE: MLServer does NOT define<br/>its own RBAC resources.<br/>All AuthN/AuthZ is handled<br/>externally by kube-rbac-proxy<br/>(RHOAI 3.x) or oauth-proxy<br/>(RHOAI 2.x legacy)"]

